cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.PF 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with a wireless network with relays and investigates the stability region and throughput performance. 
2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses the retransmission control mechanism employed by the relays, which is related to information theory. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper mentions the protocol towards self-aware networks, which is related to control systems. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper talks about multipacket reception capabilities, which is related to multimedia communication. 
5. cs.PF (Performance) - The paper analyzes the performance of the network in terms of delay and provides insights on the system performance.
